cu.explanation_en: GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_X2C changed from '192.168.70.134' to '10.0.0.1', which is in a different subnet and unreachable, causing X2-C interface routing failures.
cu.explanation_zh: GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_X2C 从 '192.168.70.134' 更改为 '10.0.0.1'，该地址位于不同子网且不可达，导致 X2-C 接口路由失败。

du.explanation_en: rsrp_ThresholdSSB changed from 19 to 0, which is below the valid range and will cause SSB detection issues, preventing proper cell selection.
du.explanation_zh: rsrp_ThresholdSSB 从 19 更改为 0，低于有效范围，将导致 SSB 检测问题，阻止正确的小区选择。
